"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yang Eui-jin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"양의진","primary":true}}]}},"person_1265629_translations":{"at":1772469969088,"data":{"id":1265629,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Angourie Rice (/æŋˈɡaʊri/; born January 1, 2001) is an Australian actress. She began her career as a child actress, coming to attention for her roles in These Final Hours and The Nice Guys. She is known for her portrayal of Betty Brant in the Marvel Cinematic Universe, appearing in Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017), Spider-Man: Far From Home (2019), and Spider-Man: No Way Home (2021). She also has appearing roles in Senior Year (2022) & the broadway adaptation of Mean Girls (2024).","name":"Angourie Rice","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"安格瑞·莱丝是一位澳大利亚女演员。曾在电影《耐撕侦探》，《蜘蛛侠：英雄归来》及续集《蜘蛛侠：英雄远征》中扮演的主要角色而闻名。","name":"安格瑞·赖斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Angourie Rice (1 de enero de 2001) es una actriz australiana protagonista en películas como These Final Hours y The Nice Guys. Es conocida por interpretar a Betty Brant en el Universo cinematográfico de Marvel en las películas Spider-Man: Homecoming y Spider-Man: Lejos de casa.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Angourie Rice (ur. 1 stycznia 2001 w Perth) – australijska aktorka, która wystąpiła m.in. w filmach \"Na pokuszenie\", \"Spider-Man: Homecoming\" i \"Nice Guys. Równi goście\".","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"앵거리 라이스","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Angourie Rice (/æŋˈɡaʊri/ ; née le 1er janvier 2001) est une actrice australienne. Elle a commencé sa carrière en tant qu'enfant actrice, se faisant remarquer pour ses rôles dans Ces dernières heures et Les gentils gars. Elle est connue pour son interprétation de Betty Brant dans l'univers cinématographique Marvel, apparaissant dans Spider-Man : Homecoming (2017), Spider-Man : Far From Home (2019) et Spider-Man : No Way Home (2021).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar","english_name":"Hungarian","data":{"biography":"Angourie Rice (Melbourne, 2001. január 1. –) ausztrál színésznő.\n\nLegismertebb alakítása Betty Brant a Marvel-moziuniverzum filmjeiben. Elsőként a 2017-es Pókember: Hazatérés című filmben tűnt fel, ezt követte a Pókember: Idegenben (2019). 2016-ban a Rendes fickók című filmben is játszott.\n\nMelbourne-ben született, Jeremy Rice rendező és Kate Rice író gyermekeként. Öt évig Perthben élt és egy évet Münchenben, majd visszatért Melbourne-be.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Анґаурі Райс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"💥Энгаури Райс. Родилась в 2001-ом году в Сиднее, Австралия. Росла в семье с младшим братом. Отец работал режиссёром, а мать была писательницей. Училась в Принцес Хилл Колледж в Мельбурне. Работает актрисой. Личную жизнь предпочитает держать в тайне\n\n🏆Главные награды🏆: Номинация на Critics Choice Awards (2024) [Дрянные девчонки]\n\n🎬Главные проекты🎬: «Человек-паук: Возвращение домой» (2017), «Общество Онор» (2022), «Дрянные девчонки» (2024)\n\n⭐Интересный факт⭐: Энгаури активно занимается литературой и даже ведёт подкаст о книгах вместе с матерью","name":"Энгаури Райс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"安格瑞·萊絲是一位澳大利亞女演員。曾在電影《黐筋雙響炮》，《蜘蛛俠：英雄歸來》及續集《蜘蛛俠：英雄遠征》中扮演的主要角色而聞名。","name":"安格瑞·賴斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ανγκάουρι Ράις","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"アンガーリー・ライス","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"安格利·萊斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"أنغوري رايس","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"แองกูรี ไรซ์","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"אנגאורי רייס","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HY","iso_639_1":"hy","name":"","english_name":"Armenian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Անգուրի Ռայս","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MK","iso_639_1":"mk","name":"","english_name":"Macedonian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Eнгaури Рајс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"انگوری رایس","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RS","iso_639_1":"sr","name":"Srpski","english_name":"Serbian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ангури Рајс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PK","iso_639_1":"ur","name":"اردو","english_name":"Urdu","data":{"biography":"","name":"انگوری رائس","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"Angourie Rice, 1 Ocak 2001 tarihinde Sidney, Avustralya'da dünyaya geldi. Yönetmen bir baba (Jeremy Rice) ve yazar bir annenin (Kate Rice) kızı olarak sanatla iç içe bir ortamda büyüdü. Ailesinin işleri nedeniyle bir süre Perth'te yaşadıktan sonra Melbourne'e yerleşti. Oyunculuk kariyerine küçük yaşlarda Avustralya yapımı kısa filmlerle başladı.\n\nProfesyonel kariyerindeki ilk önemli çıkışını, 2013 yapımı apokaliptik gerilim filmi \"Kıyamet Gecesi\" (These Final Hours) ile yaptı. Bu filmdeki performansıyla uluslararası alanda dikkat çekmeye başladı. Ancak ona asıl şöhreti getiren rol, 2016 yılında Russell Crowe ve Ryan Gosling ile birlikte rol aldığı, eleştirmenlerce beğenilen neo-noir komedi filmi \"İyi Adamlar\" (The Nice Guys) oldu. Filmde canlandırdığı Holly March karakteriyle büyük beğeni topladı ve Hollywood'un yükselen genç yetenekleri arasında gösterilmeye başlandı.\n\n2017 yılında, Sofia Coppola'nın yönettiği \"The Beguiled\" filminde yer aldı. Aynı yıl, Marvel Sinematik Evreni'ne (MCU) katılarak \"Örümcek-Adam: Eve Dönüş\" (Spider-Man: Homecoming) filminde Peter Parker'ın lise arkadaşı Betty Brant karakterini canlandırdı. Bu rolünü \"Örümcek-Adam: Evden Uzakta\" (Spider-Man: Far From Home) (2019) ve \"Örümcek-Adam: Eve Dönüş Yok\" (Spider-Man: No Way Home) (2021) filmlerinde de tekrarlayarak küresel tanınırlığını pekiştirdi.\n\n2018'de fantastik romantik drama \"Her Gün\" (Every Day) filminde başrol oynadı. Televizyon tarafında ise 2019'da \"Black Mirror\" dizisinin beşinci sezonundaki \"Rachel, Jack and Ashley Too\" bölümünde Miley Cyrus ile birlikte rol aldı. 2021 yılında, Kate Winslet'in başrolünde olduğu, eleştirmenlerce beğenilen HBO mini dizisi \"Mare of Easttown\"da, Winslet'in karakterinin kızı Siobhan Sheehan rolünü üstlendi ve bu performansıyla dramatik yönünü de güçlü bir şekilde sergiledi.\n\n2022'de Rebel Wilson'ın başrolünde olduğu Netflix komedisi \"Lise Yıllığı\" (Senior Year) filminde genç karakteri canlandırdı. 2024 yılında ise ikonik 2004 filminin müzikal uyarlaması olan \"Kötü Kızlar\" (Mean Girls) filminde Cady Heron karakteriyle başrol oynayarak kariyerindeki yükselişini sürdürdü.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_4813809_translations":{"at":1772469973856,"data":{"id":4813809,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"新月冰冰（1989年6月26日—），本名张韦，出生于四川，幼时随父母移居云南，现居于北京。中国大陆配音爱好者，主要活跃于bilibili等视频弹幕网站。代表作品有《尸兄》（小鹿）、《三毛旅行记》（巧巧）等。","name":"张韦","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Zhang Wei (张韦) is a Chinese voice actress.","name":"Zhang Wei","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"新月冰冰（1989 年 6 月 26 日—），本名張韋，出生於四川，幼時隨父母移居雲南，現居於北京。中國大陸配音愛好者，主要活躍於 bilibili 等視頻彈幕網站。代表作品有《屍兄》（小鹿）、《三毛旅行記》（巧巧）等。","name":"新月冰冰","primary":false}}]}},"person_4011252_translations":{"at":1772469979169,"data":{"id":4011252,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lee Su-mi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이수미","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"李秀美","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"李秀美","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Lee Su-mi (hangul: 이수미) es una actriz surcoreana.","name":"Lee Su-mi","primary":false}}]}},"person_1247371_translations":{"at":1772469979894,"data":{"id":1247371,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Eric Wan Tin-Chiu (Chinese: 尹天照, born 28 October 1964) is a Hong Kong television actor best known for his role as \"Fong Tin-yau\" in the My Date with a Vampire television series trilogy produced by the Hong Kong television network ATV. Wan began his acting career after graduating from the ATV Training Course in 1983. He started as a host in television programmes for children before entering the drama department. He has since acted in many films and television series.","name":"Eric Wan Tin-Chiu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"香港男演员。1984年毕业于亚洲电视第二期艺员训练班，随即主持儿童节目《500飞虎队》。80年代中期曾几次被戏剧组高层点名力捧；进入90年代，他终凭借多年来的演戏经验一步步走向男主角的位置。并出演了许多当时热播的剧集，1996年首次与林正英合作《僵尸道长Ⅱ》1998年以续集《我和僵尸有个约会》一剧吐气扬眉，成为亚视首席小生。近年，开始踏足电影界，除参与演出外，更尝试担任电影监制工作。","name":"尹天照","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"尹天照，暱稱阿照，香港男演員、前香港亞洲電視合約藝員。近年尹天照開始踏足電影界，除參與首席幕前演出外，更他在嘗試擔任電影監製工作。其影迷會為「Eric 萌友會」。","name":"尹天照","primary":true}}]}},"person_72440_translations":{"at":1772469983704,"data":{"id":72440,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"​Brendan Fehr is a Canadian film and television actor and model, best known for playing regular characters Michael Guerin on the television series \"Roswell\", Dan Cooper on \"CSI: Miami\", and Dr. Drew Alister on the medical drama \"The Night Shift\".","name":"Brendan Fehr","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","p